Here are **Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS) Interview Questions & Answers** divided into **Basic, Intermediate, and Advanced** levels with **examples and explanations**. These are useful for **DevOps / Cloud / SRE interviews**, especially if you work with **Terraform, Kubernetes, and cloud platforms** as mentioned in your previous discussions.

